          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Medical Practice Freedom Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of Health and Human Services or any state from requiring a health care provider, as a condition of the provider's licensure, to participate in a health plan or comply with requirements for meaningful use of electronic health records.</p>]]></text>
